                <p class="text-sm">Discover the top luxury watches of this year, featuring exclusive brands and timeless designs.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-black-600 hover:underline mt-4 block">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="blog-item p-6 rounded-lg bg-white text-gray-800 shadow-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/28/e9/d7/28e9d7cdee3d8452b2582e3704a5e896.jpg" alt="Blog Image" class="rounded mb-4">
